    </section>

    <!-- What the incubator does Section -->
    <section class="mt-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-800">What the incubator does:</h2>
      <div class="mt-6 space-y-6">
        <div class="flex items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              stroke="currentColor"
              class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600"
              aria-hidden="true"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="m8.25 4.5 7.5 7.5-7.5 7.5"
              />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="ml-4">
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700"><strong>Mentorship:</strong> provide support and advice around strategy, impact and direction, helping projects to massively increase their impact. This is provided through Office Hours with Paul Biggar (available 6x per week), as well as an optional dedicated mentor with a background in tech entrepreneurship and leadership.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              stroke="currentColor"
              class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600"
              aria-hidden="true"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="m8.25 4.5 7.5 7.5-7.5 7.5"
              />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="ml-4">
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700"><strong>Marketing:</strong> We help you get early users and launch to get off the ground, including connecting you to press, influencers, and ecosystem partners, as well as through our supportive community across our Discord and social media.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              stroke="currentColor"
              class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600"
              aria-hidden="true"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="m8.25 4.5 7.5 7.5-7.5 7.5"
              />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="ml-4">
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700"><strong>Volunteering:</strong> We have a database of nearly 3000 volunteers, and a dedicated recruitment team to connect them to your projects. Our most common requests are for social media coordinators, and software engineers.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              stroke="currentColor"
              class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600"
              aria-hidden="true"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="m8.25 4.5 7.5 7.5-7.5 7.5"
              />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="ml-4">
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700"><strong>Connections:</strong> We are connected to a large part of the Palestine advocacy ecosystem, and typically know the right partners who will want to help your initiative.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
