      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-800">What we expect if you join:</h2>
      <div class="mt-6 space-y-6">
        <div class="flex items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke-width="1.5"
