      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-800">Application process</h2>
      <div class="mt-6 space-y-6">
        <div class="flex items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              stroke="currentColor"
              class="w-6 h-6 text-yellow-600"
              aria-hidden="true"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="m8.25 4.5 7.5 7.5-7.5 7.5"
              />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="ml-4">
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">After you apply, we'll review your application, and invite selected projects for an interview.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              stroke="currentColor"
              class="w-6 h-6 text-yellow-600"
              aria-hidden="true"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="m8.25 4.5 7.5 7.5-7.5 7.5"
              />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="ml-4">
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">The interview: a 30 minute call, focusing on the impact you intend to have and how you intend to get there. Please don't prepare slides or a presentation.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              stroke="currentColor"
              class="w-6 h-6 text-yellow-600"
              aria-hidden="true"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="m8.25 4.5 7.5 7.5-7.5 7.5"
              />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="ml-4">
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">After the interview, we'll make a decision to admit you, and notify you as soon as possible.</p>
